What is the most important thing that every international student should bring along when coming to Singapore for the first time? 😉 
Definitely a good laptop! 
Of course you can buy one when you arrive, or how about to get a brand new MacBook for FREE? 😱😊👍 If you are 17 years old (and above) and plan to pursue your higher education in Singapore or other overseas universities, SCI has an exciting offer for you. Hurry up, as there can be only 10 lucky students! 🏃
First 10 students registered for the preparatory course for ‘A’ level will get a free MacBook and S$2000 discount off course fee❗️❗️❗️ For further information: courseinfo@spring.edu.sg,  marketing@spring.edu.sg or tel: (65) 6896 0880 or simply comment "YES" and our coordinators will contact you shortly. #specialoffer #discount #ilovetostudy #gooddeal #hugepromotion #bigpromotion #alevel #studyinsingapore #springcollegeinternational#studyabroad #studyoverseas #internationalstudents #preparatorycourse #preparationcourse #giveaway #secondaryschool #freelaptop #freemacbook
